headline: 3 Reasons SYF Has Explosive Upside Potential
summary: The past six months have been a windfall for Synchrony Financial’s shareholders. The company’s stock price has jumped 61.8%, hitting $70.90 per share. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
